  "content": "<h1 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.StoreParameter' data-commentId='T:Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.StoreParameter' id='Alis_Core_Graphic_OpenGL_Enums_StoreParameter'>Enum StoreParameter    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Graphic/src/OpenGL/Enums/StoreParameter.cs#L35'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h1>\r\n <div class=\"facts text-secondary\">\r\n<dl><dt>Namespace</dt><dd><a href='Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.html'>Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums</a></dd></dl><dl><dt>Assembly</dt><dd>Alis.dll</dd></dl>\r\n</div><p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.StoreParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The pixel store parameter enum</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public enum StoreParameter</code></pre><h2 class='section'>Fields</h2><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>UnpackSwapBytes = 3312</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.StoreParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The unpack swap bytes pixel store parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>UnpackLsbFirst = 3313</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.StoreParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The unpack lsb first pixel store parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>UnpackRowLength = 3314</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.StoreParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The unpack row length pixel store parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>UnpackSkipRows = 3315</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.StoreParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The unpack skip rows pixel store parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>UnpackSkipPixels = 3316</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.StoreParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The unpack skip pixels pixel store parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>UnpackAlignment = 3317</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.StoreParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The unpack alignment pixel store parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>PackSwapBytes = 3328</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.StoreParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The pack swap bytes pixel store parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>PackLsbFirst = 3329</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.StoreParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The pack lsb first pixel store parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>PackRowLength = 3330</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.StoreParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The pack row length pixel store parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>PackSkipRows = 3331</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.StoreParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The pack skip rows pixel store parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>PackSkipPixels = 3332</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.StoreParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The pack skip pixels pixel store parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>PackAlignment = 3333</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.StoreParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The pack alignment pixel store parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>PackSkipImages = 32875</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.StoreParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The pack skip images pixel store parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>PackSkipImagesExt = 32875</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.StoreParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The pack skip images ext pixel store parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>PackImageHeight = 32876</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.StoreParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The pack image height pixel store parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>PackImageHeightExt = 32876</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.StoreParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The pack image height ext pixel store parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>UnpackSkipImages = 32877</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.StoreParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The unpack skip images pixel store parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>UnpackSkipImagesExt = 32877</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.StoreParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The unpack skip images ext pixel store parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>UnpackImageHeight = 32878</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.StoreParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The unpack image height pixel store parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>UnpackImageHeightExt = 32878</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.StoreParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The unpack image height ext pixel store parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>PackSkipVolumesSgis = 33072</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.StoreParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The pack skip volumes sgis pixel store parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>PackImageDepthSgis = 33073</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.StoreParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The pack image depth sgis pixel store parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>UnpackSkipVolumesSgis = 33074</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.StoreParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The unpack skip volumes sgis pixel store parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>UnpackImageDepthSgis = 33075</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.StoreParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The unpack image depth sgis pixel store parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>TileWidthSgix = 33088</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.StoreParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The pixel tile width sgix pixel store parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>TileHeightSgix = 33089</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.StoreParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The pixel tile height sgix pixel store parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>TileGridWidthSgix = 33090</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.StoreParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The pixel tile grid width sgix pixel store parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>TileGridHeightSgix = 33091</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.StoreParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The pixel tile grid height sgix pixel store parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>TileGridDepthSgix = 33092</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.StoreParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The pixel tile grid depth sgix pixel store parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>TileCacheSizeSgix = 33093</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.StoreParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The pixel tile cache size sgix pixel store parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>PackResampleSgix = 33836</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.StoreParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The pack resample sgix pixel store parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>UnpackResampleSgix = 33837</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.StoreParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The unpack resample sgix pixel store parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>PackSubsampleRateSgix = 34208</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.StoreParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The pack subsample rate sgix pixel store parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>UnpackSubsampleRateSgix = 34209</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.StoreParameter.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The unpack subsample rate sgix pixel store parameter</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl>",
